---
title: Middle Eastern Chicken & Israeli Couscous with Roast Veggies, Feta Yoghurt & Pistachios
description: Grab a bowl and the largest spoon you own because you’ll want to eat as much of this nutritious chicken and veggie
couscous as possible. Enjoy root veggies like pumpkin, parsnip and beetroot roasted and spiced, they add both
a pop of colour and flavour.
